snippet.title: Dumbolf
snippet.description: Dumbolf The elephant that taught Tiger Woods how to play golf returns in the craziest minigolf game ever.

snippet.title: Dummy Never Fails
snippet.description: Dummy Never Fails Let the crash test dummy end on the right spot. Make sure to damage him as less as possible.

snippet.title: Dummy Never Fails: Community
snippet.description: Dummy Never Fails: Community Try to shoot dummy to the target with a minimum of damage to the dummy for a better score.

snippet.title: Dump Escape
snippet.description: Dump Escape Try to overcome 250 km as soon as you can transforming in, shooting at, or dodging enemies.

snippet.title: Dummy Never Fails 2
snippet.description: Dummy Never Fails 2 Use a canon to shoot dummie dolls that reach the target spot. Use as less dummies as possible.

snippet.title: Dummy Crusher
snippet.description: Dummy Crusher Use rockets and bombs to crush the dummies. Destroy all dummies to pass the level.

snippet.title: Cards Wars
snippet.description: Cards Wars Strategy game. Try to conquer the world using the highest sets of cards in this turn based game.

snippet.title: GARE: Sapphire Mechs
snippet.description: GARE: Sapphire Mechs Shooting game. End the war on the Vitris 47 planet controlling a fighter mech.

snippet.title: Star Pirate: Inception
snippet.description: Star Pirate: Inception Space shooter. Shoot and collect your way through over 12 very exciting missions in the universe.
